      "content": "Subject: Apology and Resolution for Your Espresso Machine Order\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address the delay in the shipment of your recently purchased espresso machine. We deeply regret the inconvenience this has caused, and we understand how frustrating it can be to wait for something as eagerly anticipated as your new coffee companion.\n\nOur logistics department has been working tirelessly to rectify the mistake, and we are now on track to deliver your espresso machine within the next two weeks. As a token of our sincere apologies and to make amends, we would like to offer you a 20% discount on your next purchase with us. This discount will automatically be applied to your account and can be used at your convenience.\n\nWe value your trust and loyalty, and we are committed to ensuring that your experience with us is nothing short of exceptional. If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to our customer service team.\n\nThank you for your understanding and patience. We look forward to serving you again soon.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
